    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>$(Generate_FastGraph_Core)</GeneratePackageOnBuild>

    <Title>FastGraph</Title>
    <RootNamespace>FastGraph</RootNamespace>
    <AssemblyName>FastGraph</AssemblyName>

    <!-- Overridden by CI -->
    <Version>0.0.0</Version>
    <AssemblyVersion>0.0.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>0.0.0</FileVersion>

    <Copyright>Copyright Â© 2021</Copyright>
    <Description>Provides graph structures and algorithms.

FastGraph provides generic directed/undirected graph data structures and algorithms. It comes with algorithms such as depth first seach, breath first search, A* search, shortest path, k-shortest path, maximum flow, etc...

This package is a version of the original QuickGraph (later forked as YC.QuickGraph and QuikGraph), specifically forked to support .NET 6 and C# 10.
It should be seen as an alpha-quality cutting-edge alternative to QuikGraph.</Description>
    <IsPackable>true</IsPackable>
    <PackageId>FastGraph</PackageId>
    <PackageTags>FastGraph Graph Structure Algorithm C# DAG QuickGraph QuikGraph</PackageTags>
  </PropertyGroup>

